Class URLSaxParser

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class URLSaxParser
extends AbstractSaxHandler
    Single use parser for a given url. Provides the parsing framework. Subclasses, need to provide the Sax Handling events.

      • parse

        public void parse()
           throws java.io.IOException,
                  org.xml.sax.SAXException
        Given the Url, parse it using the Html Parser, allowing the sub-class to handle all sax events.

        if the url is an http url, it will check to see that the connection status is OK before parsing, otherwise, it just passes the url into the parser and allows it parse.

        Throws:
        java.io.IOException
        org.xml.sax.SAXException
